title: Rodgers’ Comeback & Darnold’s Debut!
itunes:title: Rodgers’ Comeback & Darnold’s Debut!
description:
The Good Morning Football Crew breaks down week 1 of the NFL season and looks ahead to week 2 with Aaron Rodgers’ phenomenal comeback. The gang also discusses Sam Darnold’s rookie debut with the Jets. Lastly, Kay Adams, Nate Burleson, Peter Schrager, and Kyle Brandt take you to school with a little Journalism 101. Be sure to check in every Wednesday to the GMFB podcast! Like, share, subscribe!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
